    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em><strong>Deep Magic: </strong>Void</em><br>You infuse a pair of manacles that a creature is wearing with the mass and empty magnitude of the Void. The creature wearing the manacles gains four levels of exhaustion while restrained by them. A creature restrained by the manacles cannot gain more levels of exhaustion, and it cannot lose levels of exhaustion by finishing a long rest. The manacles can be removed by making a Dexterity (thievesâ€™ tools) check against your spell save DC. If the tools are not magical, the check is made with disadvantage. A creature can only be affected by one pair of manacles enchanted by this spell at a time.<br>Content licensed under the @UUID[Compendium.koboldpressogl.koboldpressjournal.JournalEntry.KoboldPressOGL00.JournalEntryPage.KoboldPressOGLpg]{Open Game License}",
